name: Blade Runner: Black Lotus
overview: Los Angeles 2032. A young woman wakes up with no memories, and possessing deadly skills. The only clues to her mystery are a locked data device and a tattoo of a black lotus. Putting together the pieces, she must hunt down the people responsible for her brutal and bloody past to find the truth of her lost identity.

episodes.name: City of Angels
episodes.overview: An amnesiac named Elle enters Los Angeles, carrying only a locked data device that may hold the secrets of her past.

episodes.name: All We Are Not
episodes.overview: Haunted by traumatic memories, Elle recognizes a familiar face. Upon tracking him down she uncovers a shocking truth about herself and her memories.

episodes.name: The Human Condition
episodes.overview: With help from the mysterious J, Elle learns more startling truths about the nature of her identityâ€¦

episodes.name: The Doll Hunt
episodes.overview: Elle's memories come flooding back, revealing the truth of what happened to her in the desert. Meanwhile, LAPD Officer Davis puts together the clues that will lead her to Black Lotus.

episodes.name: Pressure
episodes.overview: Elle plots her revenge with help from J, but Police Chief Grant has mobilized a massive LAPD manhunt to find and eliminate her.

episodes.name: Persistence of Memory
episodes.overview: In her quest for revenge, Elle breaks into the home of her next target and is forced to take a hostage. Chief Grant calls in reinforcements.

episodes.name: Reality
episodes.overview: After learning J's shameful secret, Elle leaves to complete her mission: to kill the last of the Doll Hunt participants.

episodes.name: The Davis Report
episodes.overview: Frustrated that no one believes her theory about Black Lotus, Officer Davis lands in hot water while presenting her findings to the department.

episodes.name: Free Will
episodes.overview: Elle goes after the final target to complete her mission of revenge, the man responsible for the Doll Hunt.

episodes.name: Clair de Lune
episodes.overview: As Elle struggles with not knowing which of her memories are real and which are artificial, J opens up about his own past.

episodes.name: All the Best Memories
episodes.overview: Desperately lost and searching for peace, Elle hatches a radical plan to put her haunted memories to rest.

episodes.name: Artificial Souls
episodes.overview: While Elle has her first encounter with a dangerous new foe, J has his final encounter with his former colleague Marlowe.

episodes.name: Time to Die
episodes.overview: Left with no other option, Elle faces off against the architect of her suffering.
